snippet.title: chekherjoy
snippet.description: Booktuber and total bookworm.  I absolutely fangirl over books, comics, movies, TV shows, music, art and anything else that tells a good story.  I'm really into Sci Fi, Fantasy, Chick Lit and Young Adult Literature.  My two main fandoms are Doctor Who and Harry Potter.  I believe in literacy, education, intersectionality, social justice and feminism.
